import React from 'react';
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row';
import TarjetaImagen from './TarjetaImagen';


function ListadoFotos(){

    return(
   
         <Row>

            <TarjetaImagen
                titulo="El Monumental"
                autor="juan"
                foto="data:image/jpeg;base64,"
                />
            <TarjetaImagen
                titulo="Paisaje"
                autor="juan"
                foto="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2020/05/06/03/46/hill-5136002__340.jpg"/>
            <TarjetaImagen
                titulo="Montañas"
                autor="juan"
                foto="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2020/01/22/22/06/wyoming-4786394__340.jpg"/>
            <TarjetaImagen
                titulo="Torta"
                autor="juan"
                foto="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2019/01/21/15/06/blueberries-3946230__340.jpg"/>
            <TarjetaImagen
                titulo="Floralis Genérica"
                autor="juan"
                foto="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2015/09/21/01/19/generic-flower-949177__340.jpg"/>
            <TarjetaImagen
                titulo="La boca"
                autor="juan"
                foto="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2014/05/22/15/51/caminito-351167__340.jpg"/>
            <TarjetaImagen
                titulo="Arboles"
                autor="juan"
                foto="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2020/05/05/17/59/river-5134258__340.jpg"/>



         </Row>
    );
}

export default ListadoFotos;
